<i>throughout the drive.</i>

01:14:30.166 --> 01:14:33.708
<i>Suddenly, your face flashed</i>
<i>in front of my eyes.</i>

01:14:34.416 --> 01:14:36.166
<i>At that moment, I felt guilty.</i>

01:14:36.750 --> 01:14:38.541
