best friend, boyfriend,

01:19:15.333 --> 01:19:17.541
ex-boyfriend, school mate,
college mate, office mate,

01:19:17.625 --> 01:19:19.666
tuition mate, bus mate,
gym mate, dance mate,

01:19:19.750 --> 01:19:22.250
